dler on one of the\n>> >nodes, it\n>> >does work just fine, but that leaves me not using SolrJ.\n>> >\n>> >Thanks,\n>> >\n>> >Mike\n>>\n>> --\n>> Sorry for being brief. Alternate email is rickleir at yahoo dot com\n\n-- \nSorry for being brief. Alternate email is rickleir at yahoo dot com \n",
